content: As an AI language model, I do not have access to real-time information or individual cases. However, generally, the time it takes to obtain a visa for the UAE can vary depending on the type of visa and the processing method applied by the embassy or consulate. Applying for a visa online usually takes around 2-3 working days, while obtaining a visa through the embassy or consulate may take longer than a week. It's advisable to check with the relevant authorities or visa processing agencies for specific information on visa processing time to avoid any inconvenience.
